			Fit Criterion & \multicolumn{2}{m{0.85\textwidth}|}{ \begin{tabular}{m{0.8\textwidth}}The player will be able to change avatar's gear by selecting the item from item's menu\end{tabular}} \\ \hline
			Satisfaction: 5 & Dissatisfaction: 5 & Priority: Medium \\ \hline
			Conflicts:N/A & \multicolumn{2}{l|}{Supporting Material:N/A} \\ \hline
